              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/20646941/" class="">第76页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/41119972/" class=" " title="希言子">希言子</a>
                (推特@XiYanZi 群己權界主義+道家)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="20646941">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
